For the hotspot scenario LFU was the clear winner
For multiple localities LFU had an advantage however it only really became obvious in larger simulations
For random access theres not super discernable upperhand in this simulation LFU falls short but if I ran it again LRU or FIFO could be the worse one. Its just random.
For sequential scenario there was a major struggle for FIFO and LRU. LFU was the only one that managed and it managed poorly. 
For temporal decay for larger programs they all managed well. When the size of the programs are lower LFU is favored but beyond that its all relatively good.

Ultimately after this project I have a more favorable opinion on LFU than the others because in most cases it was average or performed better.














